rows.label: tlk44310185_01_msg0001
rows.name: This is Teos Aure, the capital of Luxuria.

rows.label: tlk44310185_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's not often that a traveler comes
here. Mind you conduct yourself quietly
and respectfully!

rows.label: tlk44310185_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Prince Sigurd!
Please, by all means, pass through!
... Long may Teos Aure thrive!

rows.label: tlk44310185_01_msg0004
rows.name:
...Ah, but, if at all possible, would you
mind avoiding any flamboyant displays,
so as not to alarm the citizenry...?
